description:
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen to join the People Relations team. We are looking for a People Relations Advisor on a 6-month fixed term basis.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are you wanting to move to the next stage in your career in HR? Are you ready for your next challenge? If so then we would love to hear from you! We are looking for a motivated and enthusiastic person to join our People Relations Team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be joining a team where no day is the same, as such you will need to be confident working both autonomously and as part of our wider People Relations team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a People Relations Advisor, you will actively contribute to our success through the delivery of HR expertise across the Trust.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be level 5 CIPD qualified or working towards your level 5, with experience/knowledge of advising and coaching managers through a range of employee relations issues, interpreting policies and procedures with a sound knowledge of employment law. You will have excellent interpersonal and communication skills with a track record of building strong relationships.&lt;/p&gt;
